Package com.conorthomason.garageapp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attendant
    The Attendant class is used largely as a way to differentiate employee instances for the controller
    Employee
    The Employee class is superclass for both the Manager and Attendant classes.
    EmployeeManagement
    The EmployeeManagement class is the main data structure for storing the information of employees.
    Garage
    The Garage class stores the spaces, vehicles, and space counts of the Garage.
    Manager
    The Manager class is used largely as a way to differentiate employee instances for the controller
    Receipt
    Receipt class extends ticket, meant to be used when taking into account costs and time
    SingletonService
    SingletonService is used to access both the Garage and EmployeeManagement singletons throughout Android.
    Space
    The Space class is used to help in the creation of a List in the Garage class.
    Ticket
    The Ticket class is used to construct a String output when a vehicle is entered
    TimeControl
    TimeControl is intended to be used primarily for the receipt/ticket classes.
    TimeControl.Time
    Time is essentially the backend for TimeControl - it handles the thread operations.
    Utilities
    Intended for the usage of methods that are used multiple times in model.
    Vehicle
    The Vehicle class is the object stored in the main data structure.
